    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <h1>Forms</h1>
          <p class="intro">Everything should be contained within a <strong>fieldset</strong> and a <strong>field-group</strong>.</br>
            You can have multiple fieldsets within a form and multiple field-groups within a fieldset.</p>
          <p class="ui-intro">You can disable all controls within the fieldset at once, by adding <strong>disabled</strong> to it. (ie. <code>&lt;fieldset disabled&gt;</code>).</p>
          <p>
            <code>
              &lt;form&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;  &lt;fieldset&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;legend&gt;Legend&lt;/legend&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;div class="form-group"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;label for="example"&gt;Label for input&lt;/label&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;input type="email" class="form-control" id="example" placeholder="Placeholder"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;/div&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;div class="form-group"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;label for="exampleInputPassword1"&gt;Password&lt;/label&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;/div&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;div class="form-group"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;label for="exampleInputFile"&gt;File input&lt;/label&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;input type="file" id="exampleInputFile"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;p class="help-block"&gt;Example block-level help text here.&lt;/p&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;/div&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;div class="form-group"&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      &lt;button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"&gt;Submit&lt;/button&gt;</br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;    &lt;/div&gt;</br>
               &nbsp; &lt;/fieldset&gt;</br>
              &lt;/form&gt;
            </code>
          </p>
          <p><strong>Note on Columns within a form-group:</strong> Some form-groups have columns nested within them. to make them align properly you can either add a row around these columns, or for drier coding, just add the class of <strong>row</strong> to the <strong>form-group</strong> class.</p>
        </div> <!-- / col -->
      </div> <!-- / row -->
    </div> <!-- / container -->

    <!-- ========================================================================================================== -->

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <hr class="dashed-client"></hr>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h4>Form with Fieldset</h4>
          <form>
            <fieldset>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="example">Label for input</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="example" placeholder="Placeholder">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Password</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputFile">File input</label>
                <input type="file" id="exampleInputFile">
                <p class="help-block">Example block-level help text here.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <div class="checkbox">
                  <label>
                    <input type="checkbox"> Check me out
                  </label>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->

        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h4>Form with Fieldset and Legend</h4>
          <form>
            <fieldset>
              <legend>Legend</legend>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="example">Label for input</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="example" placeholder="Placeholder">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Password</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputFile">File input</label>
                <input type="file" id="exampleInputFile">
                <p class="help-block">Example block-level help text here.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <div class="checkbox">
                  <label>
                    <input type="checkbox"> Check me out
                  </label>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->

        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <hr class="dashed-client"></hr>
          <h3>Horizontal forms</h3>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->

        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h4>Form Horizontal</h4>
          <form class="form-horizontal">
            <fieldset>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="inputEmail3" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Email</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="inputEmail3" placeholder="Email">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="inputPassword3" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Password</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <input type="password" class="form-control" id="inputPassword3" placeholder="Password">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                  <div class="checkbox">
                    <label>
                      <input type="checkbox"> Remember me
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Sign in</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->

        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h4>Form Horizontal with Legend</h4>
          <form class="form-horizontal">
            <fieldset>
              <legend>Legend</legend>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="inputEmail3" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Email</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="inputEmail3" placeholder="Email">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="inputPassword3" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Password</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <input type="password" class="form-control" id="inputPassword3" placeholder="Password">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                  <div class="checkbox">
                    <label>
                      <input type="checkbox"> Remember me
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group row">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Sign in</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->
      </div> <!-- / row -->
    </div> <!-- / container -->

    <!-- ========================================================================================================== -->

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <hr class="dashed-client"></hr>
          <h3>Inline forms</h3>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->
        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <h4>Form Inline</h4>
          <form class="form-inline">
            <fieldset>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputName2">Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputName2" placeholder="Jane Doe">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputEmail2">Email</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail2" placeholder="jane.doe@example.com">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Send invitation</button>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </div> <!-- / Column -->

         <div class="col-sm-12">
          <h4>Form Inline with Legend</h4>
            <form class="form-inline">
              <fieldset>
                <legend>Legend</legend>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="exampleInputName2">Name</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputName2" placeholder="Jane Doe">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="exampleInputEmail2">Email</label>
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail2" placeholder="jane.doe@example.com">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Send invitation</button>
                </div>
              </fieldset>
            </form>
          </div> <!-- / Column -->

          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <form class="form-inline">
              <fieldset>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="sr-only" for="exampleInputEmail3">Email address</label>
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail3" placeholder="Email">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="sr-only" for="exampleInputPassword3">Password</label>
                  <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword3" placeholder="Password">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <div class="checkbox">
                    <label>
                      <input type="checkbox"> Remember me
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Sign in</button>
                </div>
              </fieldset>
            </form>
          </div> <!-- / Column -->

          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <form class="form-inline">
              <fieldset>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="sr-only" for="exampleInputAmount">Amount (in dollars)</label>
                  <div class="input-group">
                    <div class="input-group-addon">$</div>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputAmount" placeholder="Amount">
                    <div class="input-group-addon">.00</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Transfer cash</button>
                </div>
              </fieldset>
            </form>
          </div> <!-- / Column -->
      </div> <!-- / row -->
    </div> <!-- / container -->


